// material-ui
import { Timeline, TimelineItem, TimelineSeparator, TimelineConnector, TimelineContent, TimelineDot } from '@mui/lab';

// ==============================|| UI TIMELINE - RIGHT ALIGNED ||============================== //

export default function RightAlignedTimeline() {
    return (
        <Timeline position="right">
            <TimelineItem>
                <TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineDot />
                    <TimelineConnector />
                </TimelineSeparator>
                <TimelineContent>Eat</TimelineContent>
            </TimelineItem>
            <TimelineItem>
                <TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineDot />
                    <TimelineConnector />
                </TimelineSeparator>
                <TimelineContent>Code</TimelineContent>
            </TimelineItem>
            <TimelineItem>
                <TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineDot />
                    <TimelineConnector />
                </TimelineSeparator>
                <TimelineContent>Sleep</TimelineContent>
            </TimelineItem>
            <TimelineItem>
                <TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineDot />
                </TimelineSeparator>
                <TimelineContent>Repeat</TimelineContent>
            </TimelineItem>
        </Timeline>
    );
}
